    </picture>
    <div class="hero-body">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="primary-text">从技术层面上探索研究LTO</h1>
        <div class="buttons btn-container">
          <a href="https://docs.ltonetwork.com" class="button"><p class="dark-indigo">阅读文件 (EN)</p></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-top">
  <section class="section secondary no-padding">
{% include "partials/" ~ locale ~ "/promo-numbers-alt.njk" %}
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutin-top-alt cutout-bottom">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns is-vcentered inverted-mobile has-margin-top-40">
      <div class="column is-6">
         <picture>
      <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="/assets/functional-layers.webp">
          <img src="/assets/functional-layers.png" class="functional-layers lazy" alt="LTO Network - Functional Layers">
          </picture>
          </div>
       <div class="column is-5-desktop">
           <h2 class="section-title">功能层</h2>
            <div class="content">
                <strong class="muted">分散应用</strong>
                <p class="muted">组织无需节点就可以通过其节点参与分布式应用程序。</p>
                <strong class="muted">分布式数据处理</strong>
                <p class="muted">数据在特定参与者的节点之间点对点共享，而不是整个网络。</p>
                <strong class="muted">区块链</strong>
                <p class="muted">所有节点都通过公共区块链连接，以促进共识和数据完整性。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-bottom-alt" id="why-hybrid-blockchain-section">
  <section class="section alt p-top-l neg-m-top-m">
    <div class="section-body" style="position:relative;">
      <div class="private-chain-tech rellax" data-rellax-speed="2"><img src="/assets/private-chain.svg" class="lazy"  data-rellax-speed="0" alt="LTO Network - Private Chain"></div>
      <div class="public-chain-tech rellax" data-rellax-speed="-2"><img src="/assets/public-chain.svg" class="lazy" alt="LTO Network - Public Chain"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="columns">
                <div class="column is-5-desktop">
                    <h2 class="section-title deep-lavender has-text-centered-mobile">混合区块链</h2>
                        <div class="content">
                            <p class="muted">LTO允许两个或多个企业共享事件序列并达成一致。 事件共享是点对点完成的，无需依赖权威方。</p>
                            <p class="muted">参与方数量有限，在处理冲突时面临挑战。 面临冲突时，往往多数人不能做出公正的决定。</p>
                            <p class="muted">与其在网络上重新引入授权，不如通过利用我们的公共权益证明区块链来达成共识。 私有事件散列的锚定发生在公共链上。</p>
                            <p class="muted">公共链中的区块具有特定的高度，并且还对区块内的交易进行排序。 该顺序提供了全球公认的事件序列，用于在私有链上达成共识。</p>
                            <p class="muted"><em>混合区块链意味着私有数据，公众共识。</em></p>
                        </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container">
  <section class="section relative tertiary p-top-l neg-m-top-m">
           <div class="section-body">
           <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title has-text-centered">
          在LTO区块链节点内
        </h2>
        <h3 class="small-subtitle has-text-centered">
          选择任何组件以了解有关我们设置的更多信息
        </h3>
            <div class="tiles-container">
        <div class="tiles node-card">
          <div class="tile-group rest-api-layer-container">
            <span>Rest Api Layer</span>
            <div class="tile lto-node" id="api-gateway-tile">
              <span class="title is-size-6 dark-indigo">应用程序编程接口网关</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tile-group application-layer-container">
            <span>Application Layer</span>
            <div class="tile lto-node" id="event-chain-service-tile">
              <span class="title is-size-6 dark-indigo">活动链服务</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tile lto-node" id="workflow-engine-tile">
              <span class="title is-size-6 dark-indigo">其他服务</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tile-group private-chain-layer-container">
            <span>Private Chain Layer</span>
            <div class="tile lto-node" id="queuer-service-tile">
              <span class="title is-size-6 dark-indigo">消息队列服务</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tile lto-node" id="dispatcher-service-tile">
              <span class="title is-size-6 dark-indigo">分派器</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tile-group global-chain-layer-container">
            <span>全球链层</span>
            <div class="tile lto-node" id="proof-engine-tile">
              <span class="title is-size-6 dark-indigo">锚固服务</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tile-sidebar is-4 is-parent is-vertical node-card">
          <article class="tile inside-node">
            <div class="content" id="api-gateway-content" style="display: none;">
              <p class="tile-title is-size-4 title dark-indigo">应用程序编程接口网关</p>
              <div class="tile-content">
               <p class="muted">
                 API网关是一个HTTP服务器，它将所有请求代理到节点内的正确服务。</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content" id="event-chain-service-content" style="display: block;">
              <p class="tile-title is-size-4 title dark-indigo">活动链服务</p>
              <div class="tile-content">
               <p class="muted">
                  事件链服务拥有组织所涉及的所有临时专用区块链。 </p>
                <ul class="muted is-size-6">
                  <li>一个节点拥有许多临时区块链。（类似于git存储库。）</li>
                  <li>完全解耦。</li>
                  <li>可配置，使其能够与添加到应用程序的任何微服务进行交互层。</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content" id="workflow-engine-content" style="display: none;">
              <p class="tile-title is-size-4 title dark-indigo">其他服务</p>
              <div class="tile-content">
               <p class="muted">
                   可以将其他服务添加到节点以运行分散的应用程序；</p>
                <ul class="muted is-size-6">
                  <li>工作流引擎运行建模为确定性有限状态机的流程。</li>
                  <li>跨组织共享数据时，受监视的数据分发有助于达到（GDPR）法规遵从性。</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content" id="queuer-service-content" style="display: none;">
              <p class="tile-title is-size-4 title dark-indigo">消息队列服务</p>
              <div class="tile-content">
               <p class="muted">
                   队列服务提供了一个REST API来将事件排队在消息队列上。 </p>
                <ul class="muted is-size-6">
                 <li>RabbitMQ消息队列，该消息队列使用铲子将事件分发到其他节点。</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content" id="dispatcher-service-content" style="display: none;">
              <p class="tile-title is-size-4 title dark-indigo">分派器</p>
              <div class="tile-content">
               <p class="muted">
                 分派器服务解析消息队列中的消息，并将其推送到节点内的正确服务。</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content" id="proof-engine-content" style="display: none;">
              <p class="tile-title is-size-4 title dark-indigo">锚固服务</p>
              <div class="tile-content">
               <p class="muted">
                 该节点将LTO平台连接到LTO公共区块链，该区块链负责通过锚定来保护数据和事件。 
               </p>
                <ul class="muted is-size-6">
                  <li>使用行业标准的哈希（SHA2）和加密（ED25519）</li>
                  <li>算法-NG协议通常在3秒内提供快速的tx确认。</li>
                  <li>公共链针对存储哈希进行了优化，并且不提供通用功能。</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </section>
</div>

